794
01:00:29,663 --> 01:00:31,284
That's what's hurting people right now.

795
01:00:31,964 --> 01:00:37,447
So I'd rather have the discussions on how are we going to keep our tax rate low?

796
01:00:37,947 --> 01:00:40,208
How are we going to look at other revenue sources?

797
01:00:41,460 --> 01:00:44,582
Are we talking about looking at generating other revenue?

798
01:00:45,342 --> 01:01:04,112
