799
01:01:04,592 --> 01:01:10,253
So they're going to pay a higher tax rate because of the shrinking commercial base in this community.

800
01:01:10,733 --> 01:01:24,576
These are the discussions that the office of community development had, Mr. President.

801
01:01:25,136 --> 01:01:29,897
So, you know, I want to just make sure that we're sending the right message.

802
01:01:31,050 --> 01:01:37,173
And maybe this council should be sending a message that we want to entertain a proposition two and a half override.

803
01:01:37,673 --> 01:01:54,921
And that would allow a lot of people in this community to rest assure that whatever is done is according to the state statute, which is below two and a half, Mr. President, even that to many seniors is a tough pill to swallow.

804
01:01:55,895 --> 01:01:58,678
It's between getting your medicine or paying your taxes.

805
01:01:59,378 --> 01:01:59,759
Or eating.

806
01:02:00,119 --> 01:02:00,660
Or eating.

807
01:02:01,260 --> 01:02:04,143
And that's a bitter pill to swallow, Mr. President.

808
01:02:04,504 --> 01:02:05,625
And we have a lot of seniors.

809
01:02:05,685 --> 01:02:09,989
I've stated over and over again, we, Benford has a large percentage of seniors.

