818
01:02:45,629 --> 01:02:48,490
There's a lot going on, a lot of moving parts in the city.

819
01:02:49,531 --> 01:02:52,932
And I try to explain some of the modest increases that have happened.

820
01:02:53,252 --> 01:02:57,935
