822
01:03:02,820 --> 01:03:04,082
I'm not going to do business in Memphis.

823
01:03:04,102 --> 01:03:04,943
They're crazy now.

824
01:03:05,223 --> 01:03:06,625
Their tax rate's ridiculous.

825
01:03:06,865 --> 01:03:10,770
I'll just go the next town over, and we'll set up shop there.

826
01:03:11,211 --> 01:03:12,793
And that's what we're seeing, Mr. President.

827
01:03:13,485 --> 01:03:18,249
And it's unfortunate, and the burden is going to be flipped to the residential taxpayer.

828
01:03:18,609 --> 01:03:20,911
Do we need to do things in the community?

829
01:03:21,571 --> 01:03:22,132
