1050
01:21:33,415 --> 01:21:33,715
Never.

1051
01:21:34,355 --> 01:21:42,521
We're not Winchester with multiple overrides of Barbara Anderson's prop two and a half, rest her soul.

1052
01:21:43,542 --> 01:21:44,483
And nor have we done any

1053
01:21:45,670 --> 01:21:50,193
debt exclusions like Winchester High School did for their high school for $100 million.

