1081
01:24:13,937 --> 01:24:18,278
So that's why the council did not adopt it in the past, historically speaking, Mr. President.

1082
01:24:18,499 --> 01:24:19,099
Mr. President?

1083
01:24:19,499 --> 01:24:19,879
Council Bass.

