1085
01:24:31,025 --> 01:24:32,586
And this zero-sum game is killing us.

1086
01:24:32,726 --> 01:24:33,506
I don't disagree.

1087
01:24:34,006 --> 01:24:35,187
The state has set our laws.

1088
01:24:35,227 --> 01:24:38,108
